#

Peanut Butter and Banana Toast

5 min
$2.5
350 kcal
Difficulty: 10%
Servings: 1

Allergens:

Peanuts

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianNut-Free Option Available

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Breakfast

Tags:

BreakfastSnackQuickHealthy

Description

A quick and satisfying toast topped with creamy peanut butter and sweet banana slices, perfect for breakfast or a snack.

Ingredients

  • whole grain bread: 2 slices
  • peanut butter: 2 tablespoons
  • banana: 1 ripe
  • honey (optional): 1 teaspoon
  • chia seeds (optional): 1 tablespoon
